quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  22,73,"E jenumanja ŵandu! Chipelechedwe chilandanyo, basi chipikanilani. Chisimu aŵala ŵankwalumbanjilaga ŵangaŵaga Allah nganaŵa apakombwele gumba membe namuno ali atite asongangane pa jalakwejo. Soni naga membejo jili jaasombwele chindu nganaŵa achipokasisye kujalakwejo. Ali jwangali machili nkuŵenda ni nkuŵendedwa jwakwe"
  22,74,"Ngananchimbichisya Allah ni uchimbichimbi Wakwe wakum’bajila. Chisimu Allah ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwamachili gakupunda"
  22,75,"Allah akasasagulaga mitenga kuumila mwa achimalaika ni mwa ŵandu. Chisimu Allah ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakulolechesya"
  22,76,"Jukuimanya yaili paujo pao ni yapanyuma pao, soni kwa Allah pe nikwakuujila ichindu yosope"
  22,77,"E jenumanja ŵankulupilile! Jinamani soni sujuduni ni mun’galagatileje M’mbuje gwenu, soni tendagani yambone kuti m’be ŵakupunda"
  22,78,"Soni putani petala lya Allah ngondo jisyesyene. Jwalakwe ni jwansagwile ŵanganyammwe (kuŵa nkutula wambone nnope), ni nganam’bichila ŵanganyammwe mu Dini yakusausya iliyose. (Jalakweji ni) Dini ja atati ŵenu Ibrahima. Jwalakwe (Allah) ni juŵankolasile jenumanja ni lina lyakuti Asilamu, kuumila kalakose ni mu aji (Qur’an), kuti Ntenga (Muhammadi ﷺ) aŵe mboni pa jenumanja, nombe ŵanganyammwe m’be mboni pa ŵandu. Basi jimikagani Swala mwakolosya ni kutolaga Zaka, soni munkamulisyani Allah (pakola chikulupi mwa Jwalakwe, ni kun’jegama Jwelepejo). Jwalakwe ni M’mbuje gwenu. Kaje umbone nnope Ambuje ŵakwe! Soni kaje umbone nnope Akukamuchisya ŵakwe"